'''''Act of Piracy''''' ni filimi yasohotse muri 1988 yakozwe  yagati ya  [[Amerika]] na South [[Afurika y’Epfo|African]] thriller film iyoborwa  na Yohana Cardos na Star Gary Busey, Belinda Bauer na Ray Sharkey . <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090212034643/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/443933 BFI.org]</ref> Mugihe bishimira ingendo zidasanzwe muri [[Ositaraliya]], ubwato bwumuryango bufatwa [[Iterabwoba|nabaterabwoba]] . Bazwi kandi nka '''''Barracuda''''' .

== Umugambi ==
Ted Andrews ( Gary Busey ) yemeje uwahoze ari umugore we Sandy ( Belinda Bauer ) kureka abana babo Mark (Mathew Stewardson) na Tracey (Candicé Hillebrand) bamuherekeza n'umukunzi we Laura Warner (Nancy Mulford) mu rugendo mu bwato bwe buhenze cyane  muri [[Ositaraliya]], aho ateganya kugurisha ubwato.

Icyakora, nyuma yiminsi mike, biragaragara ko Laura ari umunyamuryango w’umutwe w’iterabwoba uyobowe na Jack Wilcox ( Ray Sharkey ), wifuza ko ubwato bwaba ishingiro ry’ibikorwa bye. Jack afata yacht , nuko ubwa burashimutwa , kandi kubwibyo, Mark na Tracey babikwa nkingwate.

Hamwe na Sandy, Ted atangira gushakisha  Wilcox, no gutabara Mark na Tracey.

